description: JLT Mobile Computers AB manufactures industrial personal computer. The company is headquartered in Vaxjo, Kronoberg and currently employs 30 full-time employees.  The company is engaged in the development, manufacture and marketing of onboard computers for vehicles, as well as mobile handheld tablet computers. Its product portfolio is directed towards individuals and organizations within such sectors as shipping, mining and drilling, security, military, warehouse management, construction, transportation and forestry. The Company’s computers are designed to withstand adverse environmental conditions of heavy duty applications. As of December 31, 2010, JLT Mobile Computers AB was active internationally through its two wholly-owned subsidiaries: JLT Mobile Computers Sweden AB and JLT Mobile Computers UK Ltd.
name: JLT Mobile Computers AB (publ)
